data.description: This is a special property for multi generational living. Two homes on one level all under one roof. One side has a nice covered side porch. One very  spacious bedroom and a full bath. Open floor plan for living room, kitchen with gas stove and dining area with wood floors. Large laundry room and the gun safe remains. The main living quarters has 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Beautiful kitchen/dining combination with breakfast bar and access to the covered patio. Living room with wood floors. Huge theater room. Theater seating, projector, screen, bar,  desk and shelving all remain. Large laundry room. This is situated on 5.89 private acres where the deer and turkey roam.
